{"tid":1594672,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"召集各位流亡台灣的手足","createTime":"2019-09-25T16:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T18:55:39.000Z","uid":57076,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5d067c1c2f038673be80391d42a2257b469d5e6c","tid":1594672,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9DQvio.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9DQvio.jpg&h=667c5231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請流亡台灣既手足聯絡天航<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大家唔知邊個係天航，可以去維基睇睇，佢係著名既作家，2010年已經從香港移居去台北<br />\n<br />\nfrom wiki<br />\n<br />\n自2010年起，天航移居台北，結識台灣女友E小姐，並於2012年11月求婚成功，完成畢生最大的夢想──結婚。天航於2013年3月，和E小姐結婚，由一個香港低下階層變成台灣中產。天航最喜愛的服裝是V領T恤，曾穿著「Deep V」T恤出席2011年廣州南國書香節及2012年香港書展的座談會並舉行簽名會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A9%E8%88%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%2588%25AA&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=10c13b1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A9%E8%88%AA</a><br />\n<br />\n因為天航係2010年已經移居台北，至今有9年，都有相關人脈資源可以幫台灣既手足。<br />\n<br />\n而且放心，天航既立場係企係我地手足呢邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R81Og0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR81Og0b.jpg&h=8b596af5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望係台灣既香港人可以守望相助<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67dec1f8829b079b909c972d79b17386f2808783","tid":1594672,"uid":270956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:15:46.000Z","msg":"天航fans幫推！"},{"pid":"05d1699ebe4af6dd6d17c813e4d596437d78edb5","tid":1594672,"uid":57076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25e72cd2c0437ce50de6ac21f5158dfd15ff71d","tid":1594672,"uid":57076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"另外，宜家可以從網上申請三年多次入出境證：新臺幣2000元整（約港幣$500）。<br />\n<br />\n逗留期限屆滿前，只要離開台灣一天（不能當天來回），再返回台灣，即可重獲三個月的逗留期限，直至「入出境許可證」的效期結束為止。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳細教學:<br />\n<a href=\"https://sostaiwan.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsostaiwan.com%2F&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=ea8d57bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://sostaiwan.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔明都可以揾天航了解"},{"pid":"5793ee4909eedfd7957a8ead620e2d672c272750","tid":1594672,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:23:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">自認和理非/有份參與既朋友，入黎計下分，仲有咩可以做。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"21c43f0b77d384411bf7419dbad9c09ecc0d51bd","tid":1594672,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ca3393f2acbf545d4363f4746a9582dfa0ccd8","tid":1594672,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:24:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aef0f4f1e096b410d7b3ade8035f84793cd8b3d","tid":1594672,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbe78354c0e51899018b614a0164875a6f55be8","tid":1594672,"uid":57076,"like":1,