 />\n希望係台灣既香港人可以守望相助<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T23:59:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"01be323f0d1c2a6c12cbfc44b109fea4bed94071","tid":1594672,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T00:00:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7440edc89f21e41f114cac4f75c458933bb165d4","tid":1594672,"uid":115307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T00:15:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"219ce726b12d8999b53bbb27a681a0947f6aba38","tid":1594672,"uid":234084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T00:19:41.000Z","msg":"義士唔係condom"},{"pid":"fca5ad07ee469fd637127092c1a3def4b25b800b","tid":1594672,"uid":279938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d25e72cd2c0437ce50de6ac21f5158dfd15ff71d","tid":1594672,"uid":57076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"另外，宜家可以從網上申請三年多次入出境證：新臺幣2000元整（約港幣$500）。<br />\n<br />\n逗留期限屆滿前，只要離開台灣一天（不能當天來回），再返回台灣，即可重獲三個月的逗留期限，直至「入出境許可證」的效期結束為止。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳細教學:<br />\n<a href=\"https://sostaiwan.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsostaiwan.com%2F&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=ea8d57bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://sostaiwan.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔明都可以揾天航了解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T00:29:09.000Z","msg":"2015年家人申請過，要先申請過一次正式入台證（非免費網簽或落地簽），下一次憑呢張完過嘅一次性入台證，方可申請多次證<br />\n<br />\n提供參考番"}]}